      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your pain stems from a catastrophic loss of identity that goes far beyond a setback, effectively rendering your previous life narrative null and void when the foundation of your entire existence collapses. This profound sense of hollowness suggests you are facing an existential crisis where your core self-concept has dissolved without a clear blueprint for reconstruction. While the pain of losing one's purpose is devastating, ignoring the silence is not an option; allowing yourself to fully grieve the version of yourself that no longer exists is the only honest way to begin processing this impossible reality.",
